title: On-Chain Analytics and Market Dynamics with TXMC: Episode 14
description:
Will Clemente and TXMC discuss on-chain analytics, market dynamics,  building a following, Bitcoin, and more for our weekly interview Podcast/YouTube channel series. Can now find our podcast on Spotify, Apple, and Google Podcasts as well!
